私规强加给对方，更不是不择手段遏制、打压另一方。这不是竞争，而是恶意对抗，将产生危险后果。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-6864c54bd32b66f4d52ae4d865f79dbb_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/534796380"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IzoPNyszetohcEAMaCDgxMTI1NTkwILSgwZQGMAA4N0Afcgk1MzQ3OTYzODB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "32_1653658316.8969934", "card_id": "Q_530679587", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "孩子小学不会写作文，每次写作文就词穷，不知道如何下笔，有什么好的建议提高孩子的写作能力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-26d943544f0c442df35932ad0c7cbee9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/530679587"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IzoPNyszetohcEAMaCDgwMjEwOTAzINXIr5MGMAE4LkAgcgk1MzA2Nzk1ODd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1653658316.8974395", "card_id": "Q_388150928", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "PDF 转 Word 格式乱了怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "写毕业论文没经验用 WPS 写的，是 PDF，老师要求转换成 word，我就用 WPS 中 PDF 转 word 功能转换了，结果就出现了文章页面最下面一行有些句子断开的现象，后面留了几个空格，下页有从头开始，想调整，再下页头进行删空格处理，结果竟然删掉了上页的脚注参考文献，崩溃了。求好用的 PDF 转 word 工具，可以减少格式错误的。或者像我这种情况该如何解决，谢谢大家了"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-d7391c39736e65b7d8eb1250f65e32ce_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "66 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/388150928"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IzoPNyszeto